299
00:15:54,588 --> 00:15:58,487
Yah, itu bukan ide yang cerdas.

300
00:15:58,488 --> 00:16:00,187
Hei, kau di sana!

301
00:16:00,188 --> 00:16:02,087
Hentikan ocehanmu!

302
00:16:02,088 --> 00:16:04,887
Cepat dan naiklah ke sini!

303
00:16:04,888 --> 00:16:06,387
Jadi, seperti katanya.

304
00:16:06,388 --> 00:16:08,288
Cepatlah kalian.

305
00:16:09,988 --> 00:16:11,888
Ayo, cepat.

306
00:16:15,388 --> 00:16:18,187
