312
00:16:31,288 --> 00:16:34,887
Kami bertugas 24 jam 365 hari setahun.

313
00:16:34,888 --> 00:16:37,687
Begitulah untuk kami para petugas kepolisian!

314
00:16:37,688 --> 00:16:39,787
Polisi?

315
