331
00:17:31,188 --> 00:17:32,487
Oh, yah, tidak juga...

332
00:17:32,488 --> 00:17:36,687
Anak-anak memberikan petunjuk.

333
00:17:36,688 --> 00:17:38,287
Maksudmu Conan, bukan?

334
00:17:38,288 --> 00:17:40,987
Dia memang bukan anak biasa!

335
00:17:40,988 --> 00:17:42,687
Sangat benar.

336
00:17:42,688 --> 00:17:44,287
Oh, benar.

337
00:17:44,288 --> 00:17:46,287
Aku minta maaf tentang siang ini,

338
00:17:46,288 --> 00:17:48,587
